'''Vicebaron''' was a title given to nobility. It ranked just below the rank of [[Baron/Legends|Baron]]. [[Heitor Girard|Heitor]] of [[House Girard]] and [[Sukarian]] both held the title of Vicebaron.<ref name="TOR">{{TORcite|type=class|[[Hunter (individual)|Bounty Hunter]]|Kingmaker for a Day|[[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]]}}</ref>

